{
  "stem": "3382.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To make it short--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To make it short, we opened the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I jumped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the last wagon was machine gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They shoot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right-- I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I started to go back to the territory I know is very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was going to be very careful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But to my-- to my surprise I was greeted as is-- all the time [NON-ENGLISH]-- means 'senior'-- 'Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Senior.' You know, the posture and the boots of whatever or not-- so I look like one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went, you know, through all this part of Lublin district-- crossed, forded the river, one river.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I forded the other river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Got help from peasants, who always took me for a, a, a man from the-- from the forest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had the general passport, you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which was, more or less, valid in all Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I come from far away and go far away-- is what to [? say-- ?] I would greet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Otherwise, I would greet you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I would come into your house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I would cross myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I greet, you know, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], the [? lauded ?] in our territories.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I got caught in a place called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Simply-- I was going-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I tried, you know, to, to make a shortcut and [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] encountered two German gendarmes, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they took me there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that-- their officer, drunkard, some kind of-- what, what he did-- whatever he did, he said, shoot him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Shoot him.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, they gave me a-- they gave me a shovel, took me out behind the town, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I dug out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And all the time, they drank.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were completely drunk.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
